#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have both ALSA and Open Sound System drivers installed, &kmix; will "
"use the ALSA driver."
msgstr ""
"Se tiver tanto os controladores ALSA como os do Open Sound System "
"instalados, o  &kmix; irá usar o controlador ALSA."

